0informed%20his%20career.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMorris%20Chang%20is%20a%20legend%20in%20the%20semiconductor%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20created%20the%20world's%20largest%20chipmaker%2C%20Taiwan%20Semiconductor%20Manufacturing%20Co.%20(TSMC)%2C%20which%20works%20with%20companies%20such%20as%20Apple%2C%20Nvidia%2C%20and%20Qualcomm%20and%20has%20seen%20swelling%20demand%20for%20its%20products%20amid%20the%20AI%20boom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2094%20years%20old%2C%20Chang%20has%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20%245.1%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20Forbes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20spent%20two%20decades%20at%20Texas%20Instruments%20before%20starting%20TSMC%20at%20the%20age%20of%2055.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20rarely%20gives%20interviews%20but%20has%20shared%20some%20valuable%20business%20and%20leadership%20lessons%20from%20his%20successful%20career%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f88c5bc7-2e8f-40a2-978f-6705ac3878d5%5C%22%3EOn%20getting%20promotions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChang%20was%20on%20the%20fast%20track%20at%20Texas%20Instruments%20and%20quickly%20advanced%20in%20the%20company.%20In%20a%202007%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.semi.org%2Fen%2FOral-History-Interview-Morris-Chang%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20industry%20association%20SEMI%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20key%20to%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-promoted-faster-dice-president-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esuccess%20with%20promotions%3C%2Fa%3E%20there%20was%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Baccomplished%20something%20significant%26quot%3B%20in%20each%20of%20his%20roles%2C%20including%20dramatically%20increasing%20production%20yield.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223660c6eb-029d-47aa-9d70-d6d0a9b585df%5C%22%3EOn%20taking%20risks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChang%20worked%20in%20the%20US%20for%20decades%20before%20starting%20TSMC%20in%20Taiwan.%20He%20said%20in%202007%20that%20he%20made%20the%20move%2C%20despite%20knowing%20it'd%20mean%20lower%20pay%2C%20because%20%26quot%3Bit%20was%20so%20new%2C%20and%20appeared%20to%20be%20so%20challenging.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20follow%20your%20interests%2C%20not%20where%20you%20think%20the%20big%20money%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBecause%2C%20obviously%2C%20back%20in%201985%2C%20the%20big%20money%20was%20thought%20to%20be%20in%20financial%20venture%20capital%2C%20or%20maybe%20even%20continuing%20to%20manage%20a%20company%20in%20the%20U.S.%2C%20but%20I%20felt%20that%20the%20Taiwan%20opportunity%20appealed%20to%20me%20from%20the%20interest%20point%20of%20view.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20when%20you%20don't%20chase%20money%2C%20money%20comes%20to%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227972965a-301d-4ac2-8c51-4faafa4ec812%5C%22%3EOn%20learning%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChang%20says%20learning%20by%20doing%20for%20manufacturers%20relies%20on%20centering%20production%20in%20one%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20works%2C%20the%20learning%20curve%2C%20the%20experience%20curve%2C%20it%20works%20only%20when%20you%20have%20a%20common%20location%2C%26quot%3B%20Chang%20said%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmeche.mit.edu%2Fnews-media%2Fmorris-chang-%25E2%2580%259952-sm-%25E2%2580%259953-describes-secrets-semiconductor-success%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etalk%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20MIT%20in%202023.%20%26quot%3BLearning%20is%20local.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20learning%20curve%2C%20or%20experience%20curve%2C%20which%20he's%20frequently%20touted%20in%20his%20career%2C%20is%20the%20idea%20that%20as%20you%20make%20more%20of%20something%2C%20the%20cost%20per%20unit%20goes%20down%3B%20in%20other%20words%2C%20as%20you%20become%20more%20experienced%20at%20something%2C%20you%20also%20become%20more%20efficient%20at%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f1430247-728a-45cc-90d0-aab6803bff4b%5C%22%3EOn%20workforce%20management%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChang%20shared%20a%20behind-the-scenes%20account%20of%20the%20decision-making%20that%20went%20into%20Texas%20Instruments'%20layoffs%20of%20thousands%20of%20workers%20decades%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20was%20the%20only%20person%20involved%20in%20the%20discussions%20who%20rejected%20the%20idea%20of%20using%20performance%20reviews%20to%20determine%20whose%20jobs%20would%20be%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20would%20not%20respect%20us%20if%20we%20lay%20off%20by%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFZItbr4ZJnc%26ab_channel%3DAcquired%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eepisode%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BAcquired%26quot%3B%20podcast%20in%20January%202025.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20subjective.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20separation%20expense%20is%20usually%20half%20a%20year%2C%20and%20it%20takes%20at%20least%20half%20a%20year%20to%20train%20a%20person%2C%20so%20if%20you%20need%20people%20back%20within%20a%20year%2C%20you%20shouldn't%20lay%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d5334967-1157-45ba-a108-a9b5ddf8fdce%5C%22%3EOn%20customer%20service%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChang%20believes%20TSMC's%20reputation%20for%20quality%20customer%20service%20was%20a%20factor%20in%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsmc-apple-iphone-chips-deal-history-morris-chang-intel-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprevailing%20over%20Intel%20for%20an%20iPhone%20contract%20with%20Apple%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20learned%20to%20respond%20to%20every%20request.%20Some%20of%20them%20were%20crazy%2C%20some%20of%20them%20were%20irrational%20%E2%80%94%20but%20we%20responded%20to%20each%20request%20courteously.%20Which%20we%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20in%20the%20same%20episode%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BAcquired%26quot%3B%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2237bc2dac-d179-491b-9646-0fc06