icer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoardman%2C%20who%20the%20British%20defense%20ministry%20requested%20be%20identified%20only%20by%20rank%20and%20last%20name%2C%20described%20Ukraine's%20choice%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20very%20conscious%20decision%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20huge%20quantitative%20mismatch%20to%20the%20Russian%20military%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20much%20larger%2C%20with%20more%20people%20and%20significantly%20more%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20Ukraine%20could%20have%20pushed%20for%20shorter%2C%20faster%20training%20to%20rush%20more%20soldiers%20to%20the%20front.%20Instead%2C%20it%20asked%20for%20the%20opposite%3A%20Ukraine%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHave%20them%20for%20longer%2C%20make%20them%20better.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoardman%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20idea%20is%20that%20they'll%20be%20more%20lethal%2C%20more%20effective%20when%20they%20get%20back%20to%20the%20front%20line.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d435d9ee-bb51-457b-8bfc-071044b671d7%5C%22%3EA%20'brave'%20decision%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBoardman%20said%20that%20Ukraine's%20decision%20to%20hold%20longer%20courses%20means%20fewer%20courses%20in%20a%20year%2C%20meaning%20a%20reduction%20in%20the%20number%20receiving%20training.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20more%20than%20offset%20by%20the%20increased%20quality%20of%20the%20output%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20in%20camoflage%20gear%20and%20a%20helmet%20holds%20a%20firearm%20while%20in%20a%20trench%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687e5d77f748d8c055f5f674%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkrainian%20soldiers%20training%20as%20part%20of%20Operation%20Interflex%20in%20Norway.%3Cp%3EJONATHAN%20NACKSTRAND%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20can't%20match%20Russia%20in%20force%20size%2C%20so%20it%20wants%20to%20make%20the%20troops%20it%20does%20have%20as%20lethal%20and%20effective%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Ukrainians%20have%20decided%20to%20address%20this%20by%20increasing%20the%20quality%20of%20their%20training%20in%20order%20to%20offset%20the%20quantitative%20disadvantage%2C%20which%20I%20think%20is%20a%20brave%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20Boardman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20makes%20a%20Ukrainian%20basic%20recruit%20%26quot%3Bso%20much%20better%20than%20a%20Russian%20conscript%2C%26quot%3B%20who%20may%20have%20been%20trained%20for%20just%20a%20few%20weeks%2C%20if%20not%20a%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221572522a-8614-4e3f-b2b1-3a3e6fa414a3%5C%22%3EDifferent%20from%20Russia's%20approach%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBoardman%20said%20Ukraine's%20emphasis%20on%20longer%2C%20higher-quality%20training%20stands%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20Russia's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20big%20difference%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20training%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20not%20praising%20ourselves.%20That's%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20Ukrainian's%20approach%20to%20the%20quality%20of%20their%20training%2C%20while%20the%20Russian%20training%20is%20comparatively%20short.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20Russians%20soldiers%20riding%20on%20an%20armored%20vehicle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6618fbb31caec1275a6f67e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221126%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussian%20Army%20soldiers%20ride%20their%20armoured%20vehicle%20to%20take%20positions%20and%20fire%20from%20flamethrowers%20toward%20Ukrainian%20positions%20at%20an%20undisclosed%20location%20in%20Ukraine%20in%20a%20photo%20released%20by%20Russia's%20military%20in%20April%202024.%3Cp%3ERussian%20Defense%20Ministry%20Press%20Service%20via%20AP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20Russian%20soldiers%20have%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20front%2