7-year-old%20machine%20learning%20engineer%20at%20Amazon.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20my%20Master's%20in%20Computer%20Science%20in%202011%2C%20and%20like%20others%2C%20I%20got%20tracked%20into%20coding%20as%20a%20software%20engineer.%20I%20started%20my%20career%20as%20a%20Java%20engineer%20developing%20software%20applications.%20Six%20or%20seven%20years%20later%2C%20I%20came%20across%20the%20profile%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-machine-learning%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emachine%20learning%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMachine%20learning%20was%20not%20in%20a%20boom%20at%20that%20moment.%20The%20projects%20we%20got%20were%20almost%20always%20software%20engineering%3B%20machine%20learning%20projects%20were%20really%2C%20really%20hard%20to%20get.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20college%20education%20system%20also%20hadn't%20properly%20adopted%20AI%20and%20machine%20learning%20in%20its%20curriculum.%20When%20you're%20doing%20a%20master's%20degree%20you%20can%20take%20a%20specialization%2C%20or%20you%20are%20doing%20a%20Ph.D.%20But%20what%20about%20the%20millions%20of%20software%20engineers%20who%20are%20early%20in%20their%20career%20and%20are%20not%20formally%20trained%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20thing%20I%20did%20was%20take%20some%20interest%20in%20learning%20what%20machine%20learning%20is.%20I%20grabbed%20some%20online%20free%20resources%20and%20joined%20hackathon%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20got%20my%20manager's%20attention.%20He%20hadn't%20thought%20about%20it%2C%20but%20he%20told%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BSince%20you're%20doing%20machine%20learning%2C%20we%20want%20to%20build%20something.%20Can%20you%20work%20with%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20Technically%20I%20got%20exposure%20at%20work%20itself%2C%20even%20though%20it%20wasn't%20full-blown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20ML%20is%20booming.%20Everyone%20is%20talking%20about%20ML.%20Back%20then%2C%20there%20was%20a%20fear%20that%20ML%20is%20difficult%20to%20grab%20at%20or%20difficult%20to%20get.%20They%20had%20a%20misconception%3B%20I%20had%20to%20step%20out%20of%20my%20comfort%20zone%20and%20take%20some%20initiative%20on%20my%20own%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20out%20that%20machine%20learning%20was%20another%20stream%20of%20software%20engineering.%20There's%20nothing%20magical%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20there's%20lots%20of%20exposure%20to%20it.%20You%20need%20to%20talk%20to%20your%20manager%2C%20talk%20to%20your%20PM%20or%20stakeholders%20about%20opportunities.%20That%20should%20be%20your%20first%20step.%20Directly%20coming%20out%20of%20your%20company%20and%20finding%20an%20ML%20role%20with%20only%20software%20engineering%20would%20be%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20quickest%20way%20to%20go%20in%20and%20get%20your%20hands%20dirty%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20going%20through%20online%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EML%20is%20not%20always%20the%20solution.%20It's%20one%20way%20to%20help%20you%20stay%20relevant%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20noise%20and%20there's%20a%20signal.%20On%20the%20social%20media%20platforms%20that%20everyone's%20on%2C%20you%20need%20to%20filter%20out%20the%20noise.%20You%20need%20to%20find%3A%20What%20is%20the%20innovation%20area%20that%20is%20silently%20going%20on%3F%20Which%20people%20are%20working%20to%20make%20the%20future%3F%20Those%20are%20called%20signals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESignals%20come%20from%20research%20papers%2C%20following%20leaders%2C%20following%20conferences.%20I%20followed%20that.%20I%20found%20who%20are%20the%20authenticated%20sources%20that%20can%20give%20you%20a%20glimpse%20of%20what's%20coming%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobotics-chatgpt-moment-in-the-next-few-years-vinod-khosla-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erobotics%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20to%20identify%2C%20in%20the