ttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fstart-ups%2Fmeesho-to-add-12-lakh-seasonal-jobs-ahead-of-festive-rush-125090100802_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20family%20of%204%20moved%20to%20a%20small%20town%20to%20lower%20our%20cost%20of%20living.%20As%20our%20lifestyle%20slowed%20down%2C%20we%20got%20closer%20as%20a%20family.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20family%20of%20four%20hiking%20in%20the%20mountains%20on%20a%20sunny%20day.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a5e804cfc04e97619bb342%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20his%20family%20(not%20pictured)%20moved%20for%20a%20lower%20cost%20of%20living%20but%20ended%20up%20spending%20more%20time%20together.%3Cp%3EAleksandarNakic%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20family%20moved%20from%20the%20city%20of%20Calgary%20to%20Nelson%2C%20British%20Columbia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20wife%20and%20I%20were%20juggling%20high-stress%20office%20jobs%20and%20wanted%20a%20slower%20pace%20of%20life.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20also%20wanted%20to%20lower%20our%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20and%20moving%20helped%20us%20do%20both.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20November%202017%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20did%20the%20unthinkable%3A%20We%20packed%20up%20our%20lives%20in%20Calgary%2C%20Alberta%20%E2%80%94%20a%20bustling%20metropolis%20known%20for%20its%20glass%20skyscrapers%20and%20cowboy%20hats%20%E2%80%94%20and%20moved%20to%20Nelson%2C%20British%20Columbia%2C%20a%20sleepy%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-move-mountain-town-away-from-grandparents-struggle-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emountain%20town%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20about%2011%2C000%20people%2C%20where%20you're%20more%20likely%20to%20run%20into%20someone%20carrying%20a%20yoga%20mat%20than%20a%20briefcase.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20we%20were%20both%20juggling%20high-stress%20office%20jobs%2C%20had%20two%20kids%20under%203%2C%20and%20spent%20way%20too%20much%20of%20our%20lives%20trapped%20in%20bumper-to-bumper%20hell.%20We%20were%20burned%20out%2C%20disconnected%2C%20and%20caught%20in%20the%20relentless%20churn%20of%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-city-to-small-coastal-village-better-than-suburb-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecity%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20finally%20paused%20to%20ask%20ourselves%20%3Cem%3Ewhy%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewe%20were%20living%20that%20way%2C%20the%20answer%20was%20simple%3A%20money.%20We%20needed%20to%20earn%20enough%20to%20sustain%20our%20expensive%20lifestyle%2C%20which%20meant%20working%20jobs%20that%20left%20us%20depleted%2C%20sacrificing%20our%20mental%20health%2C%20and%20rarely%20having%20quality%20time%20as%20a%20family.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20we%20made%20a%20bold%20decision%3A%20%3Cspan%3EMy%20wife%20quit%20her%20job%2C%20I%20stayed%20on%20in%20a%20remote%20position%2C%20and%20we%20left%20the%20city%20behind%20to%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-affordable-places-to-live-in-america-lowest-cost-living-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elower%20our%20cost%20of%20living%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Nelson%20was%20generally%20less%20expensive%20than%20Calgary%2C%20and%20the%20lifestyle%20changes%20we'd%20make%20by%20living%20there%20would%20also%20cut%20some%20costs%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20we%20expected%20the%20move%20to%20transform%20our%20finances%2C%20we%20weren't%20expecting%20our%20relationship%20with%20time%2C%20stress%2C%20and%20each%20other%20to%20change%20so%20much%2C%20as%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c547f030-7a65-4334-a914-351b1655cdff%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20money%20made%20sense%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20timing%20felt%20urgent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20the%20move%2C%20we%20sold%20our%20small%20three-bedroom%20duplex%20in%20Calgary%2C%20where%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Faverage-closing-costs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eour%20mortgage%20cost%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%202%2C900%20Canadian%20dollars%20a%20month%2C%20roughly%20%242%2C300%20USD%20at%20the%20time.%20Our%20daughter%2C%20then%203%2C%20was%20in%20full-time%20day%20care%20(another%20C%241%2C000-plus%20a%20month).%20Our%2011-month-old%20son%20was%20still%20in%20diapers%20and%20stayed%20at%20home%20with%20my%20wife%20before%20our%20move.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20relied%20heavily%20on%20takeout%20because%20we%20were%20too%20exhausted%20to%20cook%20or%20meal%20prep.%20With%20gas%2C%20car%20insurance%2C%20parking%20downtown%2C%20and%20all%20the%20%26quot%3Bconvenience%26quot%3B%20spending%20that%20comes%20with%20being%20short%20on%20time%2C%20we%20felt%20like%20we%20were%20treading%20water%20financially.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20started%20looking%20at%20Nelson%2C%20finding%20a%20home%20for%20our%20family%20in%20the%20idyllic%20mountain%20town%20felt%20like%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20fantasy.%20Then%20we%20came%20across%20a%20modest%20three-bedroom%20heritage%20house%20for%20rent%20at%20C%241%2C600%20a%20month%2C%20much%20less%20than%20a%20similar%20place%20would've%20cost%20us%20in%20the%20city.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20renting%20for%20a%20couple%20years%2C%20we%20bought%20a%20house%20about%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20our%20monthly%20mortgage%20is%20now%20just%20under%20C%243%2C100.%20Groceries%20cost%20about%20the%20same%20in%20Nelson%2C%20but%20we%20stopped%20eating%20out%20and%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feasy-dinners-under-30-minutes-meal-planning-recipes-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emade%20all%20our%20meals%20at%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20saving%20us%20about%20C%24300%20to%20C%24400%20monthly.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20don't%20have%20any%20childcare%20costs%2C%20as%20our%20kids%20are%20now%208%20and%2010%20and%20go%20to%20school%20full-time.%20We%20downsized%20to%20one%20vehicle%20from%20two%20and%20bought%20a%20used%20e-bike%2C%20which%20I%20use%20when%20my%20wife%20takes%20one%20kid%20to%20gymnastics%20and%20I%20need%20to%20get%20the%20other%20to%20soccer%20practice.%20And%20now%20that%20I%20work%20remotely%2C%20I%20also%20use%20the%20e-bike%20when%20running%20errands%20to%20save%20on%20parking%20and%20gas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20while%20we%20drastically%20changed%20how%20we%20spent%20our%20money%2C%20the%20biggest%20change%20was%20in%20how%20we%20spent%20our%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fb2c2e56-d6f8-4dd2-825e-7a6708aa70a9%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20days%20slowed%20down%2C%20and%20our%20connection%20deepened%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Calgary%2C%20everything%20felt%20scheduled%2C%20rushed%2C%20and%20chaotic.%20Mornings%20were%20a%20blur.%20Evenings%20were%20spent%20trying%20to%20get%20through%20the%20dinner-bath-bed%20gauntlet%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible.%20There%20were%20entire%20weeks%20when%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20barely%20had%20a%20real%20conversation%20that%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-up-to-80-percent-on-groceries-breaking-one-rule-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edidn't%20involve%20grocery%20lists%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20or%20kid%20logistics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Nelson%2C%20there%20are%20fewer%20distractions%2C%20fewer%20errands%2C%20and%20near-zero%20traffic.%20Once%20we%20were%20settled%20and%20adjusted%20to%20our%20new%20environment%2C%20we%20embraced%20the%20slower%20lifestyle%20with%20open%20arms.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20began%20eating%20dinner%20together%20every%20night.%20No%20more%20laptops%20on%20the%20counter%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-cuban-reveals-why-email-most-powerful-productivity-tool-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echecking%20emails%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20or%20working%20late%20nights%20at%20the%20office%2C%20missing%20bedtime%20with%20the%20kids.%20Afterward%2C%20we'd%20go%20for%20walks%20to%20the%20lake%20or%20hike%20in%20the%20abundance%20of%20trails%20in%20the%20woods%20skirting%20the%20town.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c2968324-fb12-4312-aeb0-1b4d42cccff7%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EWithout%20realizing%20it%2C%20we%20had%20traded%20urgency%20for%20presence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20course%2C%20our%20lifestyle%20overhaul%20wasn't%20painless%20or%20stress-free.%20There%20were%20plenty%20of%20tradeoffs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdecided-raise-kids-family-near-grandparents-pros-and-cons-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclosest%20grandparents%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20now%20live%20a%20seven-hour%20drive%20away.%20We%20can't%20call%20them%20for%20a%20quick%20babysitting%20favor%20or%20drop%20the%20kids%20off%20when%20one%20of%20us%20is%20sick.%20We%20miss%20them%20and%20our%20regular%20visits%2C%20which%20has%20been%20the%20most%20challenging%20part.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20fewer%20job%20opportunities%20here%2C%20and%20though%20we%20spend%20less%2C%20it%20took%20about%20four%20years%20for%20us%20to%20start%20saving%20again.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20we've%20also%20gained%20so%20much.%20Our%20kids%20have%20more%20freedom%20and%20get%20to%20participate%20in%20self-directed%20play%20with%20neighb