s%2C%20benefits%2C%20and%20training%20and%20development%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20reported%20pay%20rates%20are%20benchmarked%20against%20industry%20averages%20for%20US%20workers.%20That%20can%20shed%20light%20not%20just%20on%20how%20much%20employees%20earn%20in%20certain%20roles%2C%20but%20where%20a%20company%20is%20looking%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHome%20Depot%20employs%20more%20than%20470%2C000%20workers.%20It%20listed%20roughly%2020%2C000%20open%20jobs%20on%20its%20careers%20website%20as%20of%20August%2026%2C%20with%20about%202%2C200%20openings%20for%20corporate%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20H-1B%20data%2C%20most%20of%20the%20positions%20are%20based%20near%20the%20company's%20Atlanta%20headquarters%2C%20with%20additional%20roles%20in%20several%20other%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20deeper%20look%20at%20some%20of%20the%20jobs%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2252a3c88e-036b-4399-b99c-2c9dde81618d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIT%20project%20managers%20can%20earn%20%24183%2C000%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EProduct%20Manager%3A%20%2497%2C850%20to%20%24117%2C604%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESenior%20Product%20Manager%3A%20%24139%2C050%20to%20%24147%2C490%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProduct%20Management%20Manager%3A%20%24153%2C000%20to%20%24183%2C000%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222540da78-bcd9-44bc-8b76-6d56885a0b6a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EData%20scientists%20can%20earn%20more%20than%20%24216%2C000%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAssociate%20Data%20Scientist%3A%20%2496%2C176%20to%20%24110%2C000%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20Scientist%3A%20%24108%2C000%20to%20%24140%2C000%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELead%20Data%20Scientist%3A%20%24165%2C000%20to%20%24212%2C180%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20Science%20Senior%20Manager%3A%20%24165%2C900%20to%20%24216%2C000%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228d37a490-301c-4fe9-9df1-fbaa7e54e309%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOperations%20research%20analysts%20can%20nearly%20%24155%2C000%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInventory%20Planning%20Analyst%3A%20%2470%2