romotional.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20the%20company%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnike-cutting-discounts-in-2025-ceo-says-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecut%20back%20on%20markdowns%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20provide%20a%20more%20%26quot%3Belevated%26quot%3B%20experience%20beginning%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20the%20company%20said%20that%20it%20was%20planning%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnike-raising-prices-us-expects-1-billion-tariff-hit-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bsurgical%26quot%3B%20price%20hikes%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%2C%20which%20would%20roll%20out%20in%20phases%20beginning%20the%20same%20month.%20The%20company%20is%20raising%20prices%20to%20offset%20an%20expected%20%241%20billion%20cost%20increase%20from%20tariffs%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHill's%20plan%20to%20turn%20around%20Nike%20%E2%80%94%20which%20posted%20a%2010%25%20year-over-year%20sales%20decline%20for%20fiscal%202025%E2%80%94%20also%20includes%20rebuilding%20relationships%20with%20wholesale%20partners%20that%20he%20said%20were%20weakened%20by%20Nike's%20focus%20on%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnike-expands-deals-with-some-retailers-amid-dtc-shift-in-strategy-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edirect-to-consumer%20strategy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20my%20store%20visits%20are%20any%20indication%2C%20the%20company%20is%20making%20good%20on%20this%20plan.%20Here's%20what%20I%20observed%20at%20my%20local%20shoe%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20went%20to%20Nike's%20new%20location%20in%20Brooklyn.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22exterior%20of%20a%20Nike%20store%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68acb78ccfc04e97619bfa82%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20Downtown%20Brooklyn%20Nike%20store%20opened%20across%20the%20street%20from%20the%20Barclays%20Center%20in%20June%2C%20and%20I%20stopped%20in%20mid-August.%20Despite%20it%20being%20a%20rainy%20weekday%20afternoon%2C%20I%20saw%20families%20with%20their%20brown%20Nike%20bags%20exiting%20as%20I%20entered%2C%20which%20suggests%20the%20new%20location%20is%20pulling%20in%20foot%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20store%20experience%20was%20immediately%20more%20elevated%20than%20what%20I'm%20used%20to%20seeing%20at%20other%20stores%20that%20carry%20Nike%20shoes.%20The%20sprawling%20store%20was%20lined%20with%20walls%20of%20sneakers%20and%20sections%20broken%20down%20by%20gender%20and%20sport.%20The%20space%20wasn't%20lacking%20in%20square%20footage%20and%20had%20large%20displays%20that%20told%20stories%20about%20some%20of%20the%20athletes%20Nike%20works%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20Foot%20Locker%20and%20Snipes%2C%20there%20were%20no%20red%20tags%20indicating%20markdowns%20that%20I%20could%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENike's%20WNBA%20partnership%20was%20on%20full%20display.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225911%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Breanna%20Stewart%20of%20the%20New%20York%20Liberty%20drives%20past%20Bridget%20Carleton%20of%20the%20Minnesota%20Lynx%20with%20the%20basketball%20during%20Game%202%20of%20the%202024%20WNBA%20Finals.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67155c0b9b3250dbbce8a2eb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223943%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBreanna%20Stewart%20of%20the%20New%20York%20Liberty%20drives%20past%20Bridget%20Carleton%20of%20the%20Minnesota%20Lynx%20during%20Game%202%20of%20the%202024%20WNBA%20Finals.%3Cp%3EDustin%20Satloff%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Brooklyn%20Nike%20store%20is%20notably%20steps%20away%20from%20the%20Barclays%20Center%2C%20home%20to%20the%20WNBA's%20New%20York%20Liberty.%20As%20such%2C%20I%20wasn't%20surprised%20to%20see%20that%20the%20Liberty%20had%20its%20own%20display%20of%20gear%20in%20the%20store.%20Liberty%20star%20Sabrina%20Ionescu's%20shoe%20line%20was%20front%20and%20center%20in%20the%20store's%20windows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20nodded%20to%20Nike's%20decision%20to%20deepen%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnike-basketball-bet-may-be-good-news-wnba-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epartnership%20with%20the%20WNBA%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20announcing%20in%20October%20a%2012-year%20agreement%20with%20the%20NBA%2C%20WNBA%2C%20and%20NBA%20G%20League%20to%20be%20the%20exclusive%20uniform%20and%20apparel%20provider%20for%20each%20league.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20visited%202%20Foot%20Locker%20locations%20around%20New%20York%20City.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222645%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Foot%20Locker%20storefront%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b05d24194a2d49b8af5734%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221984%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20to%20a%20Brooklyn%20Foot%20Locker%20and%20another%20in%20the%20SoHo%20neighborhood%20in%20the%20last%20weeks%20of%20August.%20From%20all%20of%20my%20store%20checks%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20Foot%20Locker%20had%20the%20best%20deals%20for%20back-to-school%20shoppers.%20A%20pair%20of%20black%20and%20white%20Nike%20Dunks%2C%20for%20example%2C%20was%20marked%20down%20to%20%2475.%20At%20the%20Nike%20store%2C%20they%20were%20%24115.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Nike%20wasn't%20the%20star%20of%20the%20show%20at%20the%20Brooklyn%20Foot%20Locker%20location.%20When%20I%20walked%20in%2C%20I%20was%20met%20with%20a%20prominent%20Adidas%20display%20at%20the%20front%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%20from%20Stifel%2C%20Adidas%20is%20hitting%20its%20peak%20in%20popularity%20with%20styles%20like%20the%20retro%20Samba%20driving%20the%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdi