ude%20fashion%20retailers%20like%20Urban%20Outfitters%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faritzia-breakout-year-history-expansion-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAritzia%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20couldn't%20help%20but%20observe%20a%20New%20Balance%20section%20also%20set%20up%20in%20the%20men's%20section%20of%20the%20Urban%20Outfitters%20in%20SoHo.%20New%20Balance%20surged%20to%20second%20place%20in%20popularity%20mentions%20at%2031%25%20as%20style%20trends%20shift%20to%20retro%20running%20shoes%2C%20according%20to%20Stifel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20prices%20on%20sneakers%20varied%20from%20place%20to%20place.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Composite%20image%20of%20Nike%20Shox%20shoe%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b06094a17a8c5b4053a574%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJordan%20Hart%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20came%20across%20a%20pair%20of%20white%20and%20silver%20Nike%20Shox%20that%20cost%20%24130%20on%20sale%20at%20Foot%20Locker%2C%20%24170%20at%20the%20Nike%20store%2C%20and%20%24180%20at%20Snipes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENike%20suggests%20a%20retail%20price%20to%20wholesale%20partners%2C%20but%20they%20set%20their%20own%20prices%20and%20markdowns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20on%20the%20hunt%20for%20a%20pair%20of%20Nike%20Vomero%205s%2C%20which%20drove%20the%20fastest%20growth%20in%20popularity%20for%20boys%20and%20girls%20this%20back-to-school%20season%2C%20you'll%20be%20in%20luck.%20Every%20store%20I%20stopped%20in%20sold%20them%20in%20an%20array%20of%20colors%20at%20varying%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOverall%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20it's%20best%20to%20shop%20around%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20specific%20shoe.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222804%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nike%20shoes%20on%20display%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20s