imate%20part%20of%20it%20%E2%80%94%20the%20carbon%20dioxide%20emissions%2C%20the%20NOX%20emissions%20(harmful%20nitrogen%20oxides%20from%20fuel%20combustion)%2C%20etc%20%E2%80%94%20what%20you%E2%80%99ve%20got%20is%20someone%20grinding%20flour%20at%20Rs%2025%20a%20unit.%20Then%20again%2C%20because%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20stable%20three-phase%20power%20from%20the%20grid%2C%20they%20go%20to%20a%20mini%20grid%20operator%2C%20where%20the%20cost%20is%20prohibitive%2C%20around%20Rs%2025%20a%20unit.%20It%20eats%20into%20their%20margins.%20So%2C%20solar%20just%20makes%20sense.%20At%20DD%20Solar%20Solutions%2C%20we%20believe%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366571%2Fkalpana-sankar-hand-in-hand-india-access-to-financial-inclusion-tamil-nadu-percy-barnevik%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epowering%20livelihoods%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20empowering%20people%20to%20make%20their%20own%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tushar%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20clean%20tech%20affordable%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20convince%20someone%20about%20the%20power%20of%20the%20sun%2C%20take%20them%20to%20watch%20a%20real-life%20success%20story.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20any%20capital%20expense%2C%20it%20is%20challenging%20to%20convince%20a%20rural%20customer.%20Only%20when%20they%20see%20the%20cost-benefit%20analysis%20or%20when%20you%20compare%20the%20profits%20to%20the%20operating%20expenses%20will%20they%20see%20reason%20to%20adopt%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tushar%20adds.%20Purchasing%20a%20product%20that%20costs%20upwards%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20(a%20typical%20%3Cem%3Eatta%20chakki%3C%2Fem%3E)%20is%20not%20something%20most%20of%20them%20can%20afford%2C%20he%20reasons%2C%20pointing%20to%20how%20DD%20Solar%20Solutions%20is%20working%20with%20NBFCs%20to%20unlock%20loans%20for%20these%20customers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20we%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20earnings%20are%20about%20three%20times%20the%20monthly%20EMI.%20If%20you%20consider%20an%20oil%20expeller%20(a%20device%20that%20extracts%20oil%20from%20seeds)%2C%20the%20person%20will%20be%20making%20around%20Rs%2060%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20with%20an%20EMI%20that%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20higher%20than%20Rs%2025%2C000%20a%20month.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20needs%20to%20give%20the%20beneficiary%20economic%20peace%20of%20mind.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20trust%20with%20real-life%20examples%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Powering%20Livelihoods%20approach%20rests%20on%20the%20same%20moral%20reckoning.%20Acknowledging%20that%20early-stage%20scepticism%20is%20common%20among%20the%20adopters%20of%20clean%20tech%2C%20Abhishek%20reasons%20that%20most%20rural%20customers%20are%20not%20aware%20that%20these%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F422191%2Fagrivoltaics-projects-india-nashik-parbhani-delhi-issapur-solar-energy-generation-renewable-power%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erenewable%20technologies%20are%20capable%20of%20generating%20an%20income%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-3-1756464951.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Solar%20atta%20chakkis%20are%20part%20of%20DRE%20technologies%2C%20small-scale%2C%20clean%20energy%20systems%20that%20generate%20and%20distribute%20power%20close%20to%20the%20point%20of%20consumption%2C%20rather%20than%20depending%20on%20a%20central%20grid.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fempowering-livelihoods-3-1756464951.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%