lse%20of%20the%20market%20by%20speaking%20to%20other%20micro-preneurs%20who%E2%80%99d%20taken%20the%20leap%20from%20diesel%20to%20solar.%20He%20judges%20success%20by%20certain%20fundamental%20yardsticks%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDoes%20it%20work%20well%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20the%20efficiency%20like%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAre%20you%20happy%20with%20your%20decision%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20his%20confidence%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F282854%2Fmaharashtra-family-solar-drying-machine-food-processing-chikoo-increases-sales%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar-powered%20device%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20steady%20whirr%20of%20the%20machine%20that%20earns%20him%20Rs%2060%2C000%2Fmonth.%20After%20accounting%20for%20the%20maintenance%20costs%2C%20which%20go%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20Naveen%20says%20his%20net%20profit%20is%20around%20Rs%2050%2C000%20a%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20adapting%20technologies%20for%20a%20semi-urban%20or%20rural%20market%20is%20crucial%2C%20Tushar%20reasons.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20an%20urban%20setting%2C%20solar%20is%20more%20for%20cost%20savings.%20Battery%20storage%20isn%E2%80%99t%20as%20crucial.%20But%20this%20changes%20when%20you%20talk%20about%20a%20rural%20audience.%20They%20need%20battery%20storage.%20Then%20there%E2%80%99s%20also%20the%20part%20about%20ensuring%20that%20the%20EMIs%20are%20paid%20on%20time%20so%20that%20their%20credit%20score%20isn%E2%80%99t%20affected.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20he%20says%20financial%20literacy%20is%20key.%20DD%20Solar%20Solutions%20has%20a%20network%20of%20business%20associates%20%E2%80%94%20people%20trusted%20in%20the%20community%20%E2%80%94%20who%20see%20to%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20technology%20on%20the%20ground.%20Their%20impact%20has%20fanned%20out%20across